i think i am pretty lucky to be alive,'' said 64-year-old nick daugherty, who had come to the aid of the manager during a robbery tuesday at a cumberland farms store
manager thelma jones, 50, said the man first pointed his gun at her, demanding ``all the money.'' she refused and screamed for help from daugherty, who was stocking shelves in the back
